1
00:00:05,810 --> 00:00:08,480
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:12,135
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,135 --> 00:00:18,228
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,279 --> 00:00:24,454
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,454 --> 00:00:30,675
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,675 --> 00:00:35,961
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:35,961 --> 00:00:43,261
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,261 --> 00:00:48,285
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,285 --> 00:00:49,898
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,898 --> 00:00:55,661
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,661 --> 00:01:02,061
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,061 --> 00:01:08,528
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,528 --> 00:01:11,980
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:13,740
How about the Beijing University of Technology?

15
00:01:19,030 --> 00:01:20,400
Gao Yang,

16
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,939
the Beijing University of Technology is a bit hard for you.

17
00:01:21,939 --> 00:01:24,880
A lot of their majors require a higher score than the Tsinghua University.

18
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,139
Maybe you should choose another one.

19
00:01:26,139 --> 00:01:28,320
The Beijing University of Technology it is.

20
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:32,360
If I get into the Beijing University of Technology, can I not go abroad?

21
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,368
Fine,

22
00:01:35,368 --> 00:01:37,319
the Beijing University of Technology it is.

23
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:40,427
If you fail to get in,

24
00:01:40,427 --> 00:01:44,560
don't think about coming back after you go abroad.

25
00:02:03,134 --> 00:02:05,480
Look, isn't that Ye Xiaowen?
[Congratulations to our Track and Field Team at the National High School Competition]

26
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,239
Yes. He's so amazing now.

27
00:02:07,239 --> 00:02:08,320
Yes. Let's go.

28
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:10,019
Let's go.

29
00:02:11,850 --> 00:02:15,857
[Episode 30: I Want to be Brothers with You]

30
00:02:15,857 --> 00:02:18,139
[College Entrance Exam Countdown: 66 DAYS]

31
00:02:18,139 --> 00:02:20,560
Gao Yang.

32
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,265
You're all here?

33
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:26,199
Wait, why aren't you guys studying instead of gathering here?

34
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:27,519
We care about you.

35
00:02:27,519 --> 00:02:28,719
How did you do on the first mock exam?

36
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,876
Can you get into the Beijing University of Technology?

37
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,873
No.

38
00:02:35,579 --> 00:02:39,840
But if I keep this up, there's a good chance.

39
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:42,860
Wait, what exactly was your score?

40
00:02:48,579 --> 00:02:50,919
450.

41
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,700
Are you surprised?

42
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:58,559
I only worked hard for less than a month and I improved my score by 100.

43
00:02:58,559 --> 00:03:01,299
G-G-Gao Yang, y-y-you're awesome!

44
00:03:01,299 --> 00:03:04,440
Exactly. In that case, you'll increase 100 points by April,

45
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:06,320
another 100 points by May, by the time you take the exam in June,

46
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:08,880
you'll get 650 points!

47
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:11,000
You'll certainly get into the Beijing University of Technology.

48
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,139
- You can do it, Gao Yang.
- Calm down.

49
00:03:13,139 --> 00:03:14,559
That's not how it works.

50
00:03:14,559 --> 00:03:17,699
Gao Yang, your score is still quite far behind.

51
00:03:17,699 --> 00:03:20,334
Which subject is your weakness? Tell me and I'll tutor you.

52
00:03:21,679 --> 00:03:23,940
Well, I can't talk anymore. I have to go study.

53
00:03:23,940 --> 00:03:25,679
Take care of yourselves.

54
00:03:25,679 --> 00:03:28,000
- I'll see you at the Beijing University of Technology. Bye.
- Bye.

55
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,760
- Bye.
- Bye.

56
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:31,839
I told you I'll drink for you. Why won't you listen?

57
00:03:31,839 --> 00:03:34,020
You're not taking your own health seriously.

58
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:36,159
Enough, you've been nagging all the way home.

59
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:38,599
They are my clients. What can I do?

60
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:40,200
I'm all right. I'll be better after I take some medicine.

61
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,834
Fine. I'll make you some porridge.

62
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:07,329
Mom, take the medicine first.

63
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,564
I'm fine.

64
00:04:14,519 --> 00:04:16,653
Why are you standing here?

65
00:04:16,653 --> 00:04:19,199
You aren't going to Beijing University of Technology?

66
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:21,126
Go back to your room and study.

67
00:04:22,059 --> 00:04:23,943
Don't forget to take the medicine.

68
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,744
Xiaowen,

69
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:50,960
how was Gao Yang's score in the first mock exam?

70
00:04:53,187 --> 00:04:55,860
He only got 450.

71
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,880
- How much?
- 450.

72
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,139
- Is that a bit...
- Is it...

73
00:04:59,139 --> 00:05:01,660
Is that too much of an improvement?

74
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:05,440
Think about it, if he increases 100 points by April and another 100 points by May,

75
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:08,480
he would certainly qualify for the Beijing University of Technology in June!

76
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,639
Mr. Gao, that's not how you calculate the scores.

77
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:14,539
After he passes the threshold for first-tier colleges, every point is very hard to get.

78
00:05:14,539 --> 00:05:17,600
Xiaowen, don't worry, Gao Yang is just like me.

79
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,080
We're normally unreliable,

80
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:23,128
but we have a great explosive force at the critical moment.

81
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,459
Mr. Gao,

82
00:05:27,459 --> 00:05:32,880
you just cleaned those sneakers yesterday and the day before.

83
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:43,919
I get nervous every time I think about how you and Gao Yang

84
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:47,020
are going to take the exam soon.

85
00:05:47,020 --> 00:05:51,020
I can't help you with the exam.

86
00:05:51,020 --> 00:05:54,239
I can feel more relaxed if I do some chores.

87
00:06:00,780 --> 00:06:02,686
We still have two more months.

88
00:06:03,979 --> 00:06:05,440
Don't worry.

89
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:07,380
I'll help him.

90
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:12,600
Xiaowen, you should put more emphasis on your own studies.

91
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,619
We can do this.

92
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:20,260
The covalent bond combinations are normally more complicated.

93
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:25,461
Atoms are formed by sharing one or more pairs of electrons.

94
00:06:49,559 --> 00:06:51,159
We're looking for the value of Y.

95
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:53,580
So, we have to find the values of Y1 and Y2 first.

96
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:58,820
Y1 should be directly proportional to X, while Y2 is inversely proportional to X.

97
00:07:55,431 --> 00:08:01,579
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

98
00:08:01,579 --> 00:08:08,944
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

99
00:08:08,944 --> 00:08:14,934
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

100
00:08:14,934 --> 00:08:20,874
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

101
00:08:20,874 --> 00:08:27,526
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

102
00:08:27,526 --> 00:08:33,066
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

103
00:08:33,066 --> 00:08:37,179
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

104
00:08:37,179 --> 00:08:40,601
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

105
00:08:40,601 --> 00:08:44,061
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

106
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:49,440
Xiaowen, stop looking at that.

107
00:08:49,479 --> 00:08:53,419
We have the exam tomorrow. Take a break for a little while, okay? Stop looking at it.

108
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,360
Sit down! Sit down!

109
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,920
Stop making a row!

110
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,788
You're not taking the exam tomorrow?

111
00:09:01,859 --> 00:09:03,720
You're just in time. Sit here. Don't leave.

112
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,279
You should listen to this as well.

113
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:08,239
Mr. Wu, do we still have classes today?

114
00:09:08,239 --> 00:09:09,680
Not only are you going to have classes,

115
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,834
I'm also going to leave you some homework.

116
00:09:14,339 --> 00:09:17,659
Mr. Wu, it's our last day. Why are you giving us homework?

117
00:09:17,659 --> 00:09:19,319
What? Am I fired on the last day?

118
00:09:19,319 --> 00:09:20,640
Am I not your homeroom teacher anymore?

119
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,720
My words don't count anymore?

120
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:24,159
They do count.

121
00:09:24,159 --> 00:09:26,119
Stop screaming and howling.

122
00:09:26,119 --> 00:09:28,520
Tian Meng, pass this out to everyone in a moment.

123
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:30,399
Each of you make a wish

124
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:33,560
and write what you want to say on there.

125
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,978
Pass them out.

126
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,520
Why, Mr. Wu?

127
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,840
Can you achieve them for us?

128
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,700
Yes, I'm the Aladdin's magic lamp.

129
00:09:41,439 --> 00:09:43,368
Just write it. You'll know in a minute.

130
00:09:43,740 --> 00:09:45,340
What are you planning to write?

131
00:09:45,340 --> 00:09:48,340
- What should I write?
- I don't know. What are you writing about?

132
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:51,239
I want to marry Gao Yang.

133
00:09:51,740 --> 00:09:53,520
Xiaowen, what's your wish?

134
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:56,000
Aren't you shy at all?

135
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:25,710
[Examination Admission Ticket]

136
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,266
Gao Yang,

137
00:10:29,239 --> 00:10:31,438
do you have your exam admission ticket?

138
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,645
You're taking the college entrance exam tomorrow.

139
00:10:36,199 --> 00:10:38,699
I can't go with you.

140
00:10:38,699 --> 00:10:40,359
I just got a phone call.

141
00:10:40,359 --> 00:10:43,719
I have to go on a business trip for a conference. I have to leave now.

142
00:10:43,719 --> 00:10:46,700
Don't worry, Mom. I'm all prepared.

143
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:52,840
Students, in a moment, let's fold the paper in your hands into paper airplanes and launch our dreams into the sky, okay?

144
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,399
Okay!

145
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:56,800
Mr. Wu, you're turning this into such a formal event.

146
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,960
That's not true.

147
00:10:57,960 --> 00:11:00,039
This is not just a formal event. There's also content in there.

148
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:02,159
Are you just flying paper airplanes? No,

149
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:07,119
you are also launching your dreams and the beautiful memories of your high school life, right?

150
00:11:07,119 --> 00:11:07,960
Yes.

151
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:12,699
Mr. Wu, will the principal scold us for throwing so much paper all over the place?

152
00:11:16,479 --> 00:11:17,680
He's not off work yet?

153
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:20,840
It's okay, Old Wu. I've got your back! Let's do it!

154
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,640
Yes, we have Beibei here!

155
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:25,159
If anything happens, she'll clean it up herself, right?

156
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:27,039
All right, let's do it!

157
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:28,800
O-O-Over here!

158
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:30,168
Hurry.

159
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,800
Beibei, what did you write?

160
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:47,160
I wish my parents would stay healthy and my brother would become more docile.

161
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:48,680
Why didn't you include Gao Yang?

162
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:50,719
He got pushed back a little.

163
00:11:50,719 --> 00:11:52,359
What about you guys? What did you write?

164
00:11:52,359 --> 00:11:55,000
I wish my mom would support my writing hobby.

165
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:58,558
Hopefully, my novels can be turned into TV shows.

166
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:01,650
Jia?

167
00:12:01,650 --> 00:12:05,360
I want to go to college and be with Aunt forever.

168
00:12:12,359 --> 00:12:13,824
It's a secret.

169
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,837
What about you, Xiaowen?

170
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,509
Do our best in the exam.

171
00:12:21,339 --> 00:12:23,640
That's too simple.

172
00:12:27,139 --> 00:12:31,760
Students, let's launch our dreams into the sky!

173
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,220
Three,

174
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:34,439
two,

175
00:12:34,439 --> 00:12:36,173
one!

176
00:12:53,259 --> 00:12:55,760
Hey, good luck with the exam.

177
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:56,720
Good luck!

178
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,640
Good luck with the exam!

179
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:00,720
Good luck!

180
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,239
They're all here.

181
00:13:32,239 --> 00:13:34,119
I asked for all teachers of the senior grade.

182
00:13:34,119 --> 00:13:35,000
There are still more to come.

183
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,520
We'll mail them all to the orphanage.

184
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:37,560
These should be enough.

185
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:40,813
Mr. Gao, I want to thank you on behalf of the kids at the orphanage.

186
00:13:41,319 --> 00:13:42,880
Mr. Gao, take a break.

187
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:43,960
Aunt, you should take a break too.

188
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,520
We can do it ourselves.

189
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:47,960
Mi Jia, you can speak more and more fluently now.

190
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:50,640
Of course. I'm practicing tongue twisters lately.

191
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:53,079
How much wood would a woodchuck chuck if a woodchuck could chuck wood?

192
00:13:53,079 --> 00:13:54,439
How's that?

193
00:13:54,439 --> 00:13:56,200
- Good, good.
- That's great.

194
00:13:56,200 --> 00:14:01,480
Mr. Gao, I usually like to make little items with these fabric strips.

195
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,960
I can make good use of them this time.

196
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,560
I'll send them to the kids.

197
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:05,600
Thank you.

198
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,660
Don't thank me.

199
00:14:10,739 --> 00:14:12,439
What's going on?

200
00:14:12,439 --> 00:14:14,119
You won't answer my calls.

201
00:14:14,119 --> 00:14:16,780
W-W-What's going on?

202
00:14:20,179 --> 00:14:23,179
Is it a bad result? She didn't make it?

203
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:25,520
Beibei.

204
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,622
What?

205
00:14:27,439 --> 00:14:29,880
Are you ready?

206
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:32,339
Ready for what?

207
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:35,379
I need to repeat school, right?

208
00:14:35,379 --> 00:14:41,259
Prepare to be a healthcare professional.

209
00:14:44,339 --> 00:14:46,039
What?

210
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:53,079
Congratulations, Jin Beibei.

211
00:14:53,079 --> 00:14:58,740
You are accepted to the Nursing School of Linyang Medical University!

212
00:14:59,319 --> 00:15:00,840
Jin Beibei!
[Admission Notice]

213
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,399
I got accepted!

214
00:15:02,399 --> 00:15:05,279
Dad, that's great!

215
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:06,760
You're going to be a nurse?

216
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,239
Can you find the blood vessel?

217
00:15:08,239 --> 00:15:11,139
If I can't find it, I'll practice on you!

218
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:16,020
Jin Doudou! Why are you so annoying?

219
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:17,960
Why did you try to scare her?

220
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,379
I didn't scare her.

221
00:15:21,199 --> 00:15:27,560
By the way, actually, did Beibei decide to study medicine because of my... here?

222
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:31,219
Of course. Did you think she was doing that for Doudou's teeth?

223
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,880
What's going on?

224
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:40,560
Beibei got her admission letter.

225
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:41,760
I'll go ask them.

226
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:44,979
Uncle Gao, pick up the phone!

227
00:15:49,439 --> 00:15:51,720
Beibei, how is it? Were you accepted?

228
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:53,399
Uncle Gao, I got in!

229
00:15:53,399 --> 00:15:56,400
The Linyang Medical University accepted me!

230
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,660
Mr. Gao, please ask them about Xiaowen and I.

231
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,480
Okay.

232
00:16:02,119 --> 00:16:05,119
Beibei, what about Mi Jia and Xiaowen?

233
00:16:05,119 --> 00:16:06,760
Oh, that's right! I forgot.

234
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:09,159
Jia, you got into the Linyang Sports University!

235
00:16:09,159 --> 00:16:12,199
Xiaowen, you got into the Beijing University of Technology!

236
00:16:12,199 --> 00:16:16,279
Aunt, I got in! I can go to college, Aunt!

237
00:16:16,279 --> 00:16:19,180
- Are you happy?
- I'm so happy!

238
00:16:19,819 --> 00:16:22,720
I'm so proud of you.

239
00:16:23,259 --> 00:16:26,740
Aunt, you have to come visit me in Linyang.

240
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:32,640
Come on, let's do it.

241
00:16:35,339 --> 00:16:39,460
Jiabao, didn't your classmates get their admission letters yet?

242
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:41,119
Why is it taking so long?

243
00:16:41,119 --> 00:16:42,520
What's the rush?

244
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:44,159
Our son got such a high score.

245
00:16:44,159 --> 00:16:45,960
It's not hard to get into a college.

246
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,277
Exactly.

247
00:16:48,979 --> 00:16:51,172
- Come on.
- Hello?

248
00:16:51,172 --> 00:16:53,159
Mr. Wu!

249
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:57,700
Really?

250
00:16:57,700 --> 00:16:59,039
That's great.

251
00:16:59,039 --> 00:17:00,359
I got it.

252
00:17:00,359 --> 00:17:02,752
Thank you.

253
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:08,220
- What happened?
- Honey, our son got into the Linyang Conservatory of Music!

254
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:10,760
- Which conservatory of music?
- The one in Linyang.

255
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:11,680
You got such a high score.

256
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:14,560
Why didn't you apply for the Beijing Conservatory of Music?

257
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:15,920
I...

258
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:19,100
I wanted to be closer to home in case you miss me too much.

259
00:17:19,100 --> 00:17:20,819
You know me so well.

260
00:17:20,819 --> 00:17:21,720
So what?

261
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:23,319
You're not happy that our son is going to college in Linyang?

262
00:17:23,319 --> 00:17:24,319
I'm happy.

263
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,880
Son, what do you want for lunch?

264
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,640
I'll make it for you. All right, you don't have to say anything.

265
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:29,600
I know. I'll go make it for you now.

266
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:31,279
Mom knows me so well.

267
00:17:31,279 --> 00:17:33,359
Good, good. It's good to be close to home.

268
00:17:33,359 --> 00:17:38,059
Come on. Let me use all the hairdressing skills I learned on your head.

269
00:17:38,059 --> 00:17:42,180
All the girls in the conservatory of music will fall for your hairstyle.

270
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:44,860
Come on, what kind of hairstyle do you want?

271
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:47,479
Dad, make the middle part higher.

272
00:17:47,479 --> 00:17:49,239
Yes, it will make you look taller.

273
00:17:49,239 --> 00:17:50,960
- Dad, why are you bringing that up again?
- Fine, I won't.

274
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,520
Come on. Sit up straight.

275
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:54,779
I'll make the middle part very tall.

276
00:17:54,779 --> 00:17:59,760
Come on. To celebrate our upcoming wonderful college life, cheers!

277
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:00,640
Cheers!

278
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:02,460
Come on.

279
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:11,119
By the way, Meng, which college are you going to?

280
00:18:11,119 --> 00:18:13,560
I asked my dad and he said he didn't know.

281
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:15,039
How mysterious.

282
00:18:15,039 --> 00:18:17,279
Right, which college are you going to?

283
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:21,519
The Tsinghua University.

284
00:18:24,560 --> 00:18:26,560
What?

285
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:30,760
I just got the confirmation too. The Tsinghua University.

286
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,920
You've done so well.

287
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:34,880
At first, my score wasn't enough.

288
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:41,480
However, because I published a novel, they took an exception and accepted me.

289
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:44,000
- Let us see it.
- Let me see.
[I Don't Want To Be Brothers With You]

290
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:47,480
"I Don't Want to be Brothers with You."

291
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:50,840
I thought Xiaowen got into the best college among us,

292
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:53,620
but it's Meng instead!

293
00:18:53,620 --> 00:18:55,640
This reminds me of that awful Niu Wanwan.

294
00:18:55,640 --> 00:19:01,520
She deliberately called to brag about being accepted into a broadcasting school and that she'll see us on TV later.

295
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,560
Oh, my God.

296
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:03,800
Forget that!

297
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:06,819
Even if she's on TV, she would only get to interview you.

298
00:19:06,819 --> 00:19:08,239
You're a novelist!

299
00:19:08,239 --> 00:19:10,115
That's right.

300
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:12,389
That's great.

301
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:16,620
What's wrong with you?

302
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:18,920
Shouldn't you be happy about getting into a college?

303
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:20,939
Why are you so quiet?

304
00:19:31,439 --> 00:19:32,520
Jin Beibei.

305
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:34,460
What?

306
00:19:40,219 --> 00:19:41,640
I like you.

307
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,800
I don't like you.

308
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:56,800
Fine, I'll tell you again next time.

309
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:05,560
What are you guys doing? Let's eat now. Pick up your chopsticks.

310
00:20:08,090 --> 00:20:10,299
Start eating. Hurry up.

311
00:20:29,390 --> 00:20:34,619
- It's okay. Jiabao, I'll help you when we get to Linyang.
- Okay.

312
00:20:34,619 --> 00:20:38,379
Jia, which side are you on?

313
00:20:39,820 --> 00:20:43,920
When we get to Linyang, the three of us have to help each other.

314
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:46,219
You see, there will just be the three of us in Linyang.

315
00:20:46,219 --> 00:20:51,180
Meng, Xiaowen, and Gao Yang will all be in Beijing.

316
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:55,440
G-Gao Yang?

317
00:20:56,290 --> 00:21:01,660
Xiaowen, what about Gao Yang? Did he do well on the exam?

318
00:21:02,820 --> 00:21:05,580
Didn't Gao Yang contact you?

319
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:08,686
No.

320
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:12,358
I'll call him.

321
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:59,880
[Jinghua University of Technology]

322
00:21:59,883 --> 00:22:01,951
[Admission Letter]

323
00:22:47,060 --> 00:22:55,260
[I will go to college with Xiaowen]
[I will become the one piece man!]

324
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,540
Let's eat first.

325
00:23:26,620 --> 00:23:28,513
A chicken drumstick for each of you.

326
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:37,048
Dad,

327
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:40,531
do we have alcohol?

328
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:46,740
I'm an adult now. Before I leave, I want to have a drink with you.

329
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:37,808
Well, I didn't get into the Beijing University of Technology.

330
00:24:39,390 --> 00:24:41,375
I've let you all down.

331
00:24:58,030 --> 00:25:00,239
We saw your efforts.

332
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:03,820
You got 540 points.

333
00:25:05,070 --> 00:25:09,420
I'm so happy that I would wake up laughing. There are no regrets.

334
00:25:18,620 --> 00:25:20,457
Just you wait.

335
00:25:35,390 --> 00:25:37,336
You'll each get a computer.

336
00:25:39,250 --> 00:25:40,741
Gao Yang,

337
00:25:41,370 --> 00:25:46,720
after you go abroad, remember to stay in contact with Xiaowen.

338
00:26:33,470 --> 00:26:39,799
When I first got divorced from your mom, I was really uncertain about raising you alone.

339
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:46,461
I know you like your mom instead of me.

340
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:54,200
But I'm grateful to have you back now.

341
00:26:54,200 --> 00:27:00,625
I know this family means something to you.

342
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:12,479
They all say parents live for their children

343
00:27:13,470 --> 00:27:18,122
and they will give everything in their life for their children.

344
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:22,800
I finally understand now.

345
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:26,239
My life is only spectacular

346
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:34,804
because I have the two of you.

347
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:44,291
Gao Yang, it's all right

348
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:52,008
if you don't come back after you go abroad.

349
00:27:56,860 --> 00:27:59,320
That would give me some motivation.

350
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:02,779
I will work hard and earn enough money.

351
00:28:02,779 --> 00:28:09,900
Hopefully, I can go visit you once a year.

352
00:28:18,070 --> 00:28:19,694
Dad,

353
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:25,627
you're getting old.

354
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:29,899
I'm not old. Fill it up for me.

355
00:28:56,220 --> 00:28:57,540
Okay.

356
00:28:57,540 --> 00:29:03,620
Come on, let's drink to the Three Brothers of Tieyuan.

357
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:10,412
♫ I want to find you ♫

358
00:29:10,412 --> 00:29:15,172
♫ Let me run to you ♫

359
00:29:15,172 --> 00:29:17,012
♫ Your laughters ♫

360
00:29:17,012 --> 00:29:22,472
♫ How much are left in my heart ♫

361
00:29:22,472 --> 00:29:25,930
♫ All those sufferings ♫

362
00:29:25,930 --> 00:29:29,833
♫ Have been left in the past ♫

363
00:29:29,833 --> 00:29:34,675
♫ I'll look for the voice in the wind ♫

364
00:29:34,675 --> 00:29:39,552
♫ And I'll find you ♫

365
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:51,560
You can apply for a meal card at the cafeteria. The dormitory is in Building 3. It's that way.

366
00:29:51,560 --> 00:29:52,620
Okay, thank you.

367
00:29:52,620 --> 00:29:54,159
Have a great semester.

368
00:29:54,159 --> 00:29:56,160
- Hello, Schoolmate.
- Hello.

369
00:29:57,600 --> 00:30:00,479
You can apply for a meal card at the cafeteria. The dormitory is in Building 3.

370
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:02,700
It's all written here. Go that way.

371
00:30:02,700 --> 00:30:04,860
Okay, thank you, Senior.

372
00:30:06,070 --> 00:30:10,580
Organize a list of students from our department and hand it to our professor.

373
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:32,169
Why are you here?

374
00:30:34,470 --> 00:30:39,139
- What have you been all year?
- I repeated school for a year.

375
00:30:39,139 --> 00:30:42,500
I'm also a student of the Beijing University of Technology now.

376
00:30:44,810 --> 00:30:48,890
[Admission Letter]

377
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:53,640
You got into the Beijing University of Technology?

378
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:56,420
Of course. I'm so smart.

379
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:03,219
Why are you just sitting there? Let's go through the procedures.

380
00:31:05,170 --> 00:31:07,079
I'm sorry, Schoolmate.

381
00:31:07,079 --> 00:31:10,879
This isn't the School of Economics. You've come to the wrong place.

382
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:15,999
It's been a year. Why are you still like this? What kind of attitude is that?

383
00:31:15,999 --> 00:31:18,413
Why didn't you make Gao Yang go abroad?

384
00:31:19,930 --> 00:31:23,030
If he has a future here, why should he go abroad?

385
00:31:23,030 --> 00:31:24,364
Thank you.

386
00:31:25,010 --> 00:31:27,640
Thank you for giving Gao Yang another chance.

387
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:31,460
All right, stop nagging. You guys go ahead with the procedures. I'm leaving.

388
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:34,125
You're leaving so soon?

389
00:31:34,125 --> 00:31:37,360
I have to feed a whole office of people. Do you think I'm an idler like you?

390
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:39,363
Yes, yes.

391
00:31:39,363 --> 00:31:42,800
Although you've been unreliable all your life,

392
00:31:42,800 --> 00:31:46,636
you did make one reliable decision, which was to bring Xiaowen home.

393
00:31:46,636 --> 00:31:51,720
That's for sure. I'm very good at making big decisions.

394
00:31:54,390 --> 00:31:55,500
I'm leaving.

395
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:57,017
Bye.

396
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:08,619
Why didn't you tell me about repeating school?

397
00:32:08,619 --> 00:32:10,499
I was trying to surprise you.

398
00:32:14,250 --> 00:32:18,779
Where are your roommates from? How are you getting along with them? Did anyone bully you?

399
00:32:18,779 --> 00:32:24,240
Watch your tone. Show some respect. Call me Senior.

400
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:26,639
I'm older than you, okay?

401
00:32:26,639 --> 00:32:29,439
I don't care. I'm one grade higher than you. You have to call me Senior.

402
00:32:29,439 --> 00:32:32,600
No way. You're my younger brother. You'll always be my younger brother.

403
00:32:32,600 --> 00:32:36,219
Even when we're in college, we are still brothers, understand?

404
00:32:36,219 --> 00:32:39,419
[The End]

405
00:32:55,890 --> 00:33:02,090
