409
00:33:21,485 --> 00:33:28,137
♫ I don't fear how rough the journey might be I will no longer run away ♫

410
00:33:28,137 --> 00:33:33,777
♫ Maybe I'm meant to be on the road Go ♫

411
00:33:33,777 --> 00:33:37,690
♫ Chase your wishes ♫

412
00:33:37,690 --> 00:33:41,012
♫ Set sail for your dreams ♫

413
00:33:41,012 --> 00:33:44,407
♫ Don't leave any regret in your youth ♫

414
00:33:44,407 --> 00:33:51,067
Team Credits

415
00:33:51,067 --> 00:33:54,378
♫ Find the answer through the crazies path ♫

416
00:33:54,378 --> 00:33:58,490
♫ Break the storm with the bravest heart ♫

417
00:33:58,490 --> 00:34:02,310
♫ I'll flap my wings to fly to the future ♫
